{
  "texts": [
    "Nie et al. (2021) proposes a KB-aware NER framework which incorporates KB knowledge to via type projection to alleviate heterogeneity between KB knowledge and NER type scheme.",
    "Fu et al. (2023) proposes a dictionarybased method that recognizes biomedical entities from input text via synonym generalization.",
    "However, such dictionary-based methods yet fail to generalize over multiple domains.",
    "In this paper, we present VERIFINER, a verification framework that identifies errors from existing NER methods and revises them into more faithful predictions via knowledge-grounded reasoning.",
    "It is the first attempt to solve NER with verification."
  ]
}